{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":609610,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":126451,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"晚安","timestamp":1606237345,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":2,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":126451,"reply":1,"tag":null,"text":"晚安好梦。\n今天开始读耶胡达·阿米亥的诗。\n\u003e我进入你时，是以精准的剧痛\n度量伟大爱情的唯一方式。\n苦涩而又粗暴。\n……\n而我们成长得离爱情越远，\n就被迫谈得越多，\n说那些话，那些长长的拼凑的句子。\n假如我们一直都在一起，\n我们可能会沉默。\n——摘自《苦涩而粗暴》","timestamp":1606237319,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782654,"url":"","vote":{}}}